title: A'One 'Leo Lights' EP
description: When her team needs her, A'ja Wilson delivers. Every. Single. Time. This radiant A'One, inspired by her zodiac sign, celebrates the born leader A'ja was destined to be. Underfoot, plush Cushlon 3.0 foam provides unapologetic comfort, helping to keep her fresh all game and to shine every way the moment demands. Because when the spotlight's on, A'ja owns it. With its extra-durable rubber outsole, this version gives you traction for outdoor courts.
